Gamers are having a hard item finding a GPU for their gaming rigs as prices are soaring due to demand from cryptocurrency miners. Reuters is reporting that the NVIDIA GeForce 1070 GPU was selling for $349 a year ago and is now being sold on Amazon for up to $900 by resellers due to the demand for the graphics card and the low inventory..
