NVIDIA stock climbed 6% in early trading last week after 14 different Wall Street brokerages raised price targets on the NVIDIA stock because of their confidence in the sector. Normally gamers use the video cards for playing video games, but hardware has been popular with the cryptocurrency mining set, eating up inventory and driving prices up..
